node.text: I would love my fans to check this out. My daughter, SOPHIA, has Come up with a really wonderful BOOK CLUB. For those people that love the written word hopefully will support this project ! One of the main reason I made it was I learned so much about life by always reading … Thank you ! Keep punching and keep reading , Remember knowledge is power. @favoritebookclub

node.text: I walked into my office and almost scared myself. This amazing sculpture of “Barney Ross” from EXPENDABLES ,  was done by a brilliant artist named Howard Senft @howardsstudios , Incredible work my friend thank you very much, I guess now I have to do another sequel!
